        <abstract>
            <p>Mentions his Plutonic view of earth history.</p>
            <p>Cites Lyell’s opinions on loess.</p>
            <p>CD doubts contemporaneousness of extinct great animals with ice period.</p>
            <p>Cites applicability of Forbes’s theory of glacier structure to structure of volcanic obsidian.</p>
            <p>CD is falling astern in the geological race for knowledge.</p>
        </abstract>
